  <h2>Rutas segГәn el comando</h2>

  <table>
    <tr><th>Comando</th><th>Pipeline</th></tr>
    <tr><td><code>forja archivo.fa</code></td><td>Lexer вҶ’ Parser вҶ’ Type Checker вҶ’ Borrow Checker вҶ’ <strong>Transpilador</strong> вҶ’ .rs</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>forja run archivo.fa</code></td><td>Lexer вҶ’ Parser вҶ’ Type Checker вҶ’ <strong>Bytecode вҶ’ VM</strong> вҶ’ Output</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>forja repl</code></td><td>Por lГӯnea: Lexer вҶ’ Parser вҶ’ <strong>Bytecode вҶ’ VM</strong> (variables persisten)</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>forja build archivo.fa</code></td><td>Lexer вҶ’ Parser вҶ’ Type Checker вҶ’ <strong>Bytecode вҶ’ AOT</strong> вҶ’ .exe</td></tr>
  </table>

  <h2>Fases del pipeline</h2>

  <table>
    <tr><th>Fase</th><th>MГіdulo</th><th>Entrada</th><th>Salida</th></tr>
